@startuml
title GoF Pattern : Memento + Observer

note as GoFLabel
  **<<Memento + Observer>>**
end note

class Document {
  + id: int
  + content: string
  + save(): void
}
interface Memento {
  + getState(): any
}
class DocumentMemento {
}
class DocumentEditor {
  + document: Document
  + save(): void
  + restoreMemento(Memento m): void
}
class Toolbar {
}
class StatusBar {
}
class PreviewPanel {
}

DocumentEditor --> Document
DocumentEditor *--> Toolbar
DocumentEditor *--> StatusBar
DocumentEditor *--> PreviewPanel
Toolbar ..> Document
StatusBar ..> Document
PreviewPanel ..> Document
GoFLabel .. Document
@enduml